Package org.apache.hadoop.hbase.namespace

Class NamespaceTableAndRegionInfo

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.namespace.NamespaceTableAndRegionInfo
@Private class NamespaceTableAndRegionInfo extends Object
NamespaceTableAndRegionInfo is a helper class that contains information about current state of tables and regions in a namespace.
